<p id="mwAe4">랭크의 크기는 최대 <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt100" data-mw="{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;math&quot;,&quot;attrs&quot;:{},&quot;body&quot;:{&quot;extsrc&quot;:&quot;n&quot;}}" id="mwAe8"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle n}">
