</section><section data-mw-section-id="10" id="mwAgU" aria-labelledby="역사"><div class="mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id="역사"><span id=".EC.97.AD.EC.82.AC" typeof="mw:FallbackId"></span>역사</h2><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="//ko.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=%EC%A0%91%EB%AF%B8%EC%82%AC_%EB%B0%B0%EC%97%B4&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10" title="부분 편집: 역사"><span>편집</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p id="mwAgY">접미사 배열은 원래 <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gene_Myers?action=edit&amp;redlink=1" title="Gene Myers (없는 문서)" class="new" typeof="mw:LocalizedAttrs" id="mwAgc" data-mw-i18n="{&quot;title&quot;:{&quot;lang&quot;:&quot;x-page&quot;,&quot;key&quot;:&quot;red-link-title&quot;,&quot;params&quot;:[&quot;Gene Myers&quot;]}}">Gene Myers</a>와 <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/Udi_Manber?action=edit&amp;redlink=1" title="Udi Manber (없는 문서)" class="new" typeof="mw:LocalizedAttrs" id="mwAgg" data-mw-i18n="{&quot;title&quot;:{&quot;lang&quot;:&quot;x-page&quot;,&quot;key&quot;:&quot;red-link-title&quot;,&quot;params&quot;:[&quot;Udi Manber&quot;]}}">Udi Manber</a>가 <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/접미사_트리" title="접미사 트리" id="mwAgk">접미사 트리</a>보다 메모리 소비를 줄이려고 개발하였다. 이 경향이 이어져 압축된 접미사 배열이나 압축 전문 인덱스 등이 개발되었다.</p>

</section><section data-mw-section-id="11" id="mwAgo" aria-labelledby="같이_보기"><div class="mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id="같이_보기"><span id=".EA.B0.99.EC.9D.B4_.EB.B3.B4.EA.B8.B0" typeof="mw:FallbackId"></span>같이 보기</h2><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="//ko.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=%EC%A0%91%EB%AF%B8%EC%82%AC_%EB%B0%B0%EC%97%B4&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11" title="부분 편집: 같이 보기"><span>편집</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<ul id="mwAgs"><li id="mwAgw"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/접미사_트리" title="접미사 트리" id="mwAg0">접미사 트리</a></li></ul>

</section><section data-mw-section-id="12" id="mwAg4" aria-labelledby="참고_문헌"><div class="mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id="참고_문헌"><span id=".EC.B0.B8.EA.B3.A0_.EB.AC.B8.ED.97.8C" typeof="mw:FallbackId"></span>참고 문헌</h2><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="//ko.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=%EC%A0%91%EB%AF%B8%EC%82%AC_%EB%B0%B0%EC%97%B4&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12" title="부분 편집: 참고 문헌"><span>편집</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
